Pacifix quickly turned in front of Slag, trying to use the large frame
of his side to stop the Dinobot. "No Slag, stand down." he said in a
firm voice. " I brought him because we don't know what were up against,
but whatever it is i'm sure Slag can withstand it. Besides, he might
learn something.
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Hoist stepped towards Gesper. "Would you like a tour of the base? Or
perhaps to see firsthand what is happening at this city." He then
started to head into the ship, waiting.
